<section class="section">
  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <p>
    Pointer files keep your Git history lean, while the clean/smudge filters interact
    with Arweave. Uploads leverage ArDrive Turbo for speed, and downloads use the
    public gateway so developers can clone without a wallet. References are stored
    in `repository/.git/info/arweave-lfs-refs.json` to avoid duplicate uploads.
  </p>
</section>

